{"type":"user","uuid":"9938448d-80e6-42bf-a959-17f37da15716","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_dc38175a98ef45ecacad0fbe","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-002: Telegram Pipeline Command Router\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→在 Telegram Bot 中新增管道控制命令路由层，支持解析与分发 `/pipeline`、`/bugfix`、`/planner`、`/status`、`/logs`、`/stop` 等命令，将参数规范化后交给后端控制模块执行。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 命令语义解析、参数验证、权限检查、路由分发。不包含长任务执行。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-001 (Project Infrastructure Setup) — completed\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: Pipeline Command\n  16→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/pipeline [action] [target]` 命令启动或查询 feature 管道。\n  17→\n  18→**Example**:\n  19→- `/pipeline run my-feature` — 启动管道\n  20→- `/pipeline status` — 查询状态\n  21→- `/pipeline logs my-feature` — 查看日志\n  22→\n  23→**Acceptance**:\n  24→- 支持 `run`, `status`, `logs`, `stop` 子命令\n  25→- `target` 参数可选，默认当前工作目录\n  26→- 无效子命令返回帮助提示\n  27→\n  28→---\n  29→\n  30→### US-2: Bugfix Command\n  31→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/bugfix [target]` 快捷命令启动 bugfix 管道。\n  32→\n  33→**Example**:\n  34→- `/bugfix session-123` — 启动 bugfix 管道\n  35→\n  36→**Acceptance**:\n  37→- 等同于 `/pipeline run --type=bugfix <target>`\n  38→- 参数缺失时返回使用说明\n  39→\n  40→---\n  41→\n  42→### US-3: Status Query\n  43→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/status` 查看当前管道状态。\n  44→\n  45→**Example**:\n  46→- `/status` — 显示所有运行中的管道\n  47→\n  48→**Acceptance**:\n  49→- 返回管道列表 + 状态摘要\n  50→- 无运行管道时返回提示\n  51→\n  52→---\n  53→\n  54→### US-4: Logs Query\n  55→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/logs [target]` 查看管道日志。\n  56→\n  57→**Example**:\n  58→- `/logs` — 最近管道日志\n  59→- `/logs session-123` — 指定目标日志\n  60→\n  61→**Acceptance**:\n  62→- 支持分页或截断显示\n  63→- 日志过长时发送为文件\n  64→\n  65→---\n  66→\n  67→### US-5: Stop Pipeline\n  68→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/stop [target]` 停止运行中的管道。\n  69→\n  70→**Example**:\n  71→- `/stop` — 停止当前管道\n  72→- `/stop session-123` — 停止指定管道\n  73→\n  74→**Acceptance**:\n  75→- 确认停止操作\n  76→- 返回停止结果\n  77→\n  78→---\n  79→\n  80→### US-6: Error Guidance\n  81→作为用户，当我输入错误参数时，系统返回明确的修正建议。\n  82→\n  83→**Example**:\n  84→- `/pipeline xyz` → \"未知子命令 'xyz'。可用: run, status, logs, stop\"\n  85→\n  86→**Acceptance**:\n  87→- 参数错误有明确提示\n  88→- 提供正确的命令示例\n  89→\n  90→---\n  91→\n  92→### US-7: Authorization Guard\n  93→作为未授权用户，我无法调用管道命令，且收到统一拒绝提示。\n  94→\n  95→**Acceptance**:\n  96→- 所有管道命令需授权检查\n  97→- 统一拒绝消息（不暴露敏感信息）\n  98→\n  99→---\n 100→\n 101→## Non-Functional Requirements\n 102→\n 103→### NFR-1: Extensibility\n 104→- 命令路由层支持注册新命令\n 105→- 参数解析器可扩展\n 106→\n 107→### NFR-2: Testability\n 108→- Handler 接口可 mock\n 109→- 权限检查可 mock\n 110→\n 111→### NFR-3: Performance\n 112→- 命令解析 < 50ms\n 113→- 不阻塞 Telegram webhook\n 114→\n 115→---\n 116→\n 117→## Scope Boundaries\n 118→\n 119→### In Scope\n 120→- 命令解析与路由\n 121→- 参数规范化\n 122→- 权限检查\n 123→- 帮助文本生成\n 124→- 错误提示\n 125→\n 126→### Out of Scope\n 127→- 长任务执行（由 pipeline-control-service 处理）\n 128→- Pipeline 内部逻辑\n 129→- 持久化存储\n 130→- Web UI\n 131→\n 132→---\n 133→\n 134→## Command Reference\n 135→\n 136→| Command | Subcommands | Params | Handler |\n 137→|---------|-------------|--------|---------|\n 138→| `/pipeline` | run, status, logs, stop | `[target]`, `[--type=]` | pipelineHandler |\n 139→| `/bugfix` | — | `<target>` | bugfixHandler |\n 140→| `/planner` | run, status, logs | `[target]` | plannerHandler |\n 141→| `/status` | — | — | statusHandler |\n 142→| `/logs` | — | `[target]` | logsHandler |\n 143→| `/stop` | — | `[target]` | stopHandler |\n 144→\n 145→---\n 146→\n 147→## Alias Mapping\n 148→\n 149→| Alias | Maps To |\n 150→|-------|---------|\n 151→| `/p` | `/pipeline` |\n 152→| `/b` | `/bugfix` |\n 153→| `/s` | `/status` |\n 154→| `/l` | `/logs` |\n 155→\n 156→---\n 157→\n 158→## Open Questions\n 159→\n 160→[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q1: `/planner` 命令的完整行为是什么？是否需要独立管道类型？\n 161→\n 162→[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q2: 权限检查是否复用现有的 `isAllowedUser()`，还是需要分级权限？\n 163→\n 164→[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q3: 日志过长时是否需要分页机制，还是直接发送文件？\n 165→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde2c2d14f97954bce470f362c09e","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:34:22.836Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312023422fed03f1c7d3749cc","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"id":"20260312023422fed03f1c7d3749cc","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_49ca33159439466aa285730a","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/002-telegram-pipeline-command-router/spec.md","new_string":"## Decisions\n\n| ID | Date | Decision |\n|----|------|----------|\n| D1 | 2026-03-12 | `/planner` 为独立管道类型，行为同 `/pipeline`，默认 `type=planner` |\n| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 复用现有 `isAllowedUser()` 进行授权检查，分级权限留作后续扩展 |\n| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 日志 < 4000 字符分块发送，>= 4000 字符发送为文件 |","old_string":"## Open Questions\n\n[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q1: `/planner` 命令的完整行为是什么？是否需要独立管道类型？\n\n[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q2: 权限检查是否复用现有的 `isAllowedUser()`，还是需要分级权限？\n\n[NEEDS CLARIFICATION] Q3: 日志过长时是否需要分页机制，还是直接发送文件？","replace_all":false}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":27010,"output_tokens":496,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde2c2d14f97954bce470f362c09e","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:34:42.264Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"adcc3560-d6a3-4c98-a7d9-736a63430b3e","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_49ca33159439466aa285730a","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully edited file: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/002-telegram-pipeline-command-router/spec.md"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde2c2d14f97954bce470f362c09e","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:34:42.270Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120234420f697913612d44e4","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"id":"202603120234420f697913612d44e4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Step 2: prizmkit.plan → 创建 plan.md\n\n现在创建技术实施计划，包含架构设计、接口设计和数据模型。"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde2c2d14f97954bce470f362c09e","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:36:02.127Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120234420f697913612d44e4","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"id":"202603120234420f697913612d44e4","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_4563c83143f847fa9bcf74b4","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# F-002: Technical Implementation Plan\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Telegram Bot Entry                       │\n│                   src/bot/telegram.js                        │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   Command Router Layer                       │\n│              src/bot/commands/index.js                       │\n│  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐      │\n│  │   Parser     │  │   Registry   │  │  Validator   │      │\n│  │ parseCommand │  │ commandMap   │  │ validateArgs │      │\n│  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Command Handlers                          │\n│                 src/bot/commands/handlers/                   │\n│  ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌──────────┐ │\n│  │ pipeline   │ │ bugfix     │ │ status     │ │ logs     │ │\n│  │ Handler    │ │ Handler    │ │ Handler    │ │ Handler  │ │\n│  └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └──────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                              │\n                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Pipeline Control Service (F-001)                │\n│          src/services/pipeline-control-service.js            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Component Design\n\n### 1. Command Parser (`src/bot/commands/parser.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 解析 Telegram 消息文本为结构化命令对象。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface ParsedCommand {\n  command: string;      // e.g., \"pipeline\"\n  subcommand?: string;  // e.g., \"run\"\n  args: string[];       // positional args\n  options: Record<string, string>; // --key=value\n  raw: string;          // original text\n}\n\nfunction parseCommand(text: string): ParsedCommand | null;\n```\n\n**Logic**:\n1. 提取命令名（第一个 token，去掉 `/`）\n2. 解析别名映射\n3. 提取子命令（如果有）\n4. 解析 `--key=value` 选项\n5. 收集位置参数\n\n---\n\n### 2. Command Registry (`src/bot/commands/registry.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 注册命令及其元数据，支持动态扩展。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface CommandMeta {\n  name: string;\n  aliases: string[];\n  subcommands?: string[];\n  params: ParamMeta[];\n  requiresAuth: boolean;\n  helpText: string;\n}\n\ninterface ParamMeta {\n  name: string;\n  required: boolean;\n  description: string;\n}\n\nfunction registerCommand(meta: CommandMeta, handler: CommandHandler): void;\nfunction getCommand(name: string): CommandEntry | null;\nfunction getHelpText(command?: string): string;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Command Validator (`src/bot/commands/validator.js`)\n\n**Purpose**: 验证命令参数，生成错误提示。\n\n**Interface**:\n```typescript\ninterface ValidationResult {\n  valid: boolean;\n  errors: ValidationError[];\n  normalized?: NormalizedParams;\n}\n\ninterface ValidationError {\n  param: string;\n  message: string;\n  suggestion?: string;\n}\n\nfunction validateCommand(parsed: ParsedCommand, meta: CommandMeta): ValidationResult;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. Command Handlers\n\n#### Pipeline Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js`)\n\n```typescript\ninterface PipelineParams {\n  action: 'run' | 'status' | 'logs' | 'stop';\n  target?: string;\n  type?: 'feature' | 'bugfix' | 'planner';\n}\n\nasync function handlePipeline(ctx: Context, params: PipelineParams): Promise<void>;\n```\n\n**Mapping to pipeline-control-service**:\n- `run` → `startPipeline({ pipelineType, targetId })`\n- `status` → `getPipelineStatus({})`\n- `logs` → `getPipelineLogs({ targetId })`\n- `stop` → `stopPipeline({ targetId })`\n\n#### Bugfix Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/bugfix.js`)\n\n```typescript\nasync function handleBugfix(ctx: Context, target: string): Promise<void> {\n  // Delegates to handlePipeline with type=bugfix\n  return handlePipeline(ctx, { action: 'run', target, type: 'bugfix' });\n}\n```\n\n#### Status Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`)\n\n```typescript\nasync function handleStatus(ctx: Context): Promise<void> {\n  // Calls getPipelineStatus({}) and formats output\n}\n```\n\n#### Logs Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`)\n\n```typescript\nasync function handleLogs(ctx: Context, target?: string): Promise<void> {\n  // Calls getPipelineLogs({ targetId })\n  // If output >= 4000 chars, send as file\n}\n```\n\n#### Stop Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js`)\n\n```typescript\nasync function handleStop(ctx: Context, target?: string): Promise<void> {\n  // Calls stopPipeline({ targetId })\n  // Shows confirmation\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Models\n\n### CommandDefinition\n```typescript\ninterface CommandDefinition {\n  name: string;\n  aliases: string[];\n  description: string;\n  usage: string;\n  examples: string[];\n  subcommands?: SubcommandDefinition[];\n  params?: ParamDefinition[];\n  requiresAuth: boolean;\n}\n```\n\n### SubcommandDefinition\n```typescript\ninterface SubcommandDefinition {\n  name: string;\n  description: string;\n  params?: ParamDefinition[];\n}\n```\n\n### ParamDefinition\n```typescript\ninterface ParamDefinition {\n  name: string;\n  type: 'string' | 'number' | 'enum';\n  required: boolean;\n  default?: any;\n  enum?: string[];\n  description: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Command Definitions\n\n### /pipeline\n```yaml\nname: pipeline\naliases: [p]\nsubcommands:\n  - name: run\n    params:\n      - name: target\n        type: string\n        required: false\n        description: 目标标识符\n      - name: type\n        type: enum\n        enum: [feature, bugfix, planner]\n        default: feature\n  - name: status\n  - name: logs\n    params:\n      - name: target\n        type: string\n        required: false\n  - name: stop\n    params:\n      - name: target\n        type: string\n        required: false\n```\n\n### /bugfix\n```yaml\nname: bugfix\naliases: [b]\nparams:\n  - name: target\n    type: string\n    required: true\n# Equivalent to: /pipeline run --type=bugfix <target>\n```\n\n### /planner\n```yaml\nname: planner\naliases: []\nsubcommands:\n  - name: run\n    params:\n      - name: target\n        type: string\n        required: false\n  - name: status\n  - name: logs\n# Equivalent to: /pipeline run --type=planner <target>\n```\n\n### /status\n```yaml\nname: status\naliases: [s]\n# Shows all running pipelines\n```\n\n### /logs\n```yaml\nname: logs\naliases: [l]\nparams:\n  - name: target\n    type: string\n    required: false\n```\n\n### /stop\n```yaml\nname: stop\nparams:\n  - name: target\n    type: string\n    required: false\n```\n\n---\n\n## Module Dependencies\n\n```\nsrc/bot/commands/\n├── index.js          # Router entry point\n├── parser.js         # Command parsing\n├── registry.js       # Command registration\n├── validator.js      # Parameter validation\n├── formatter.js      # Output formatting\n├── help.js           # Help text generation\n└── handlers/\n    ├── pipeline.js\n    ├── bugfix.js\n    ├── planner.js\n    ├── status.js\n    ├── logs.js\n    └── stop.js\n\nDependencies:\n├── src/services/pipeline-control-service.js (F-001)\n├── src/security/guard.js (existing)\n└── src/utils/logger.js (existing)\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Specification\n\n### Router API (`src/bot/commands/index.js`)\n\n```typescript\n// Main router function\nexport async function routeCommand(ctx: Context): Promise<boolean>;\n\n// Returns true if command was handled, false otherwise\n// Handles auth check, parsing, validation, and dispatch\n```\n\n### Handler Interface\n\n```typescript\ninterface CommandHandler {\n  (ctx: Context, params: Record<string, any>): Promise<void>;\n}\n\ninterface HandlerContext {\n  ctx: Context;           // Telegram context\n  parsed: ParsedCommand;  // Parsed command\n  meta: CommandMeta;      // Command metadata\n  reply: (text: string) => Promise<void>;\n  replyFile: (content: string, filename: string) => Promise<void>;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Error Types\n\n| Code | Message | Example |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| `UNKNOWN_COMMAND` | 未知命令 '{cmd}'。输入 /help 查看可用命令。 | `/xyz` |\n| `UNKNOWN_SUBCOMMAND` | 未知子命令 '{sub}'。可用: {list} | `/pipeline xyz` |\n| `MISSING_PARAM` | 缺少参数 '{param}'。用法: {usage} | `/bugfix` |\n| `INVALID_PARAM` | 参数 '{param}' 无效: {reason} | `/pipeline run --type=xyz` |\n| `UNAUTHORIZED` | 当前账号未被授权使用该命令。 | 未授权用户 |\n\n### Error Response Format\n\n```typescript\ninterface ErrorResponse {\n  code: string;\n  message: string;\n  suggestion?: string;\n  usage?: string;\n}\n\nfunction formatError(error: ErrorResponse): string;\n```\n\n---\n\n## Test Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Module | Test Cases |\n|--------|------------|\n| `parser.js` | 解析各种命令格式、别名、选项 |\n| `registry.js` | 注册、查找、别名映射 |\n| `validator.js` | 必填参数、类型检查、枚举值 |\n| `handlers/*.js` | Mock pipeline-control-service，验证调用参数 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Scenario | Test |\n|----------|------|\n| E2E command flow | 模拟 Telegram 消息，验证完整流程 |\n| Auth guard | 验证未授权用户被拦截 |\n| Error messages | 验证错误消息格式 |\n\n### Test Files\n\n```\ntests/bot/commands/\n├── parser.test.js\n├── registry.test.js\n├── validator.test.js\n├── handlers/\n│   ├── pipeline.test.js\n│   ├── bugfix.test.js\n│   └── status.test.js\n└── integration/\n    └── command-router.test.js\n```\n\n---\n\n## Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|--------|------------|\n| 命令解析错误 | Medium | Medium | 完善测试覆盖，提供清晰错误提示 |\n| 权限绕过 | Low | High | 统一权限检查层，避免遗漏 |\n| 性能阻塞 | Low | Medium | 确保解析轻量，长操作异步 |\n| 命令冲突 | Low | Low | Registry 检查重复注册 |\n\n---\n\n## User Story Mapping\n\n| User Story | Components | Tasks |\n|------------|------------|-------|\n| US-1: Pipeline | parser, registry, pipeline-handler | T-100 |\n| US-2: Bugfix | parser, registry, bugfix-handler | T-101 |\n| US-3: Status | parser, registry, status-handler | T-102 |\n| US-4: Logs | parser, registry, logs-handler | T-103 |\n| US-5: Stop | parser, registry, stop-handler | T-104 |\n| US-6: Error Guidance | validator, formatter | T-105 |\n| US-7: Authorization | registry (requiresAuth) | T-010 |\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/002-telegram-pipeline-command-router/plan.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":27543,"output_tokens":2831,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde2c2d14f97954bce470f362c09e","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:36:02.138Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
