{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120238574cf53b2a9b4747f9","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"id":"202603120238574cf53b2a9b4747f9","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde3215a3feaab491438fa1cc8800","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/002-telegram-pipeline-command-router/spec.md","old_string":"### US-1: Pipeline Command\n作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/pipeline [action] [target]` 命令启动或查询 feature 管道。\n\n**Example**:\n- `/pipeline run my-feature` — 启动管道\n- `/pipeline status` — 查询状态\n- `/pipeline logs my-feature` — 查看日志\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 支持 `run`, `status`, `logs`, `stop` 子命令\n- `target` 参数可选，默认当前工作目录\n- 无效子命令返回帮助提示","new_string":"### US-1: Pipeline Command\n作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/pipeline [action] [target]` 命令启动或查询 feature 管道。\n\n**Note**: `/planner` 命令作为 `/pipeline` 的管道类型变体（type=planner），行为相同，故包含在本 US 范围内（见 D1）。\n\n**Example**:\n- `/pipeline run my-feature` — 启动管道\n- `/pipeline status` — 查询状态\n- `/pipeline logs my-feature` — 查看日志\n- `/planner run my-feature` — 启动 planner 类型管道\n\n**Acceptance**:\n- 支持 `run`, `status`, `logs`, `stop` 子命令\n- `target` 参数可选，默认当前工作目录\n- 无效子命令返回帮助提示\n- `/planner` 行为等同于 `/pipeline --type=planner`"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde31bb7ddbe279d381bdf6cd76fd","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:39:53.373Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
