{"type":"assistant","uuid":"202603120241219fad1dd326d143b8","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"id":"202603120241219fad1dd326d143b8","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_718b082da8f94013834830d2","name":"Glob","input":{"pattern":"tests/**/*.test.js"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":21855,"output_tokens":318,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde33ed3f9bdc09c71e868513fe14","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:41:30.162Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"51019471-3fa1-43d2-bdbf-7e0e345c8ac0","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_aa76cab3e4c24d1083beeadc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-002: Telegram Pipeline Command Router\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→在 Telegram Bot 中新增管道控制命令路由层，支持解析与分发 `/pipeline`、`/bugfix`、`/planner`、`/status`、`/logs`、`/stop` 等命令，将参数规范化后交给后端控制模块执行。\n   6→\n   7→**Scope**: 命令语义解析、参数验证、权限检查、路由分发。不包含长任务执行。\n   8→\n   9→**Dependencies**: F-001 (Project Infrastructure Setup) — completed\n  10→\n  11→---\n  12→\n  13→## User Stories\n  14→\n  15→### US-1: Pipeline Command\n  16→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/pipeline [action] [target]` 命令启动或查询 feature 管道。\n  17→\n  18→**Note**: `/planner` 命令作为 `/pipeline` 的管道类型变体（type=planner），行为相同，故包含在本 US 范围内（见 D1）。\n  19→\n  20→**Example**:\n  21→- `/pipeline run my-feature` — 启动管道\n  22→- `/pipeline status` — 查询状态\n  23→- `/pipeline logs my-feature` — 查看日志\n  24→- `/planner run my-feature` — 启动 planner 类型管道\n  25→\n  26→**Acceptance**:\n  27→- 支持 `run`, `status`, `logs`, `stop` 子命令\n  28→- `target` 参数可选，默认当前工作目录\n  29→- 无效子命令返回帮助提示\n  30→- `/planner` 行为等同于 `/pipeline --type=planner`\n  31→\n  32→---\n  33→\n  34→### US-2: Bugfix Command\n  35→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/bugfix [target]` 快捷命令启动 bugfix 管道。\n  36→\n  37→**Example**:\n  38→- `/bugfix session-123` — 启动 bugfix 管道\n  39→\n  40→**Acceptance**:\n  41→- 等同于 `/pipeline run --type=bugfix <target>`\n  42→- 参数缺失时返回使用说明\n  43→\n  44→---\n  45→\n  46→### US-3: Status Query\n  47→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/status` 查看当前管道状态。\n  48→\n  49→**Example**:\n  50→- `/status` — 显示所有运行中的管道\n  51→\n  52→**Acceptance**:\n  53→- 返回管道列表 + 状态摘要\n  54→- 无运行管道时返回提示\n  55→\n  56→---\n  57→\n  58→### US-4: Logs Query\n  59→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/logs [target]` 查看管道日志。\n  60→\n  61→**Example**:\n  62→- `/logs` — 最近管道日志\n  63→- `/logs session-123` — 指定目标日志\n  64→\n  65→**Acceptance**:\n  66→- 支持分页或截断显示\n  67→- 日志过长时发送为文件\n  68→\n  69→---\n  70→\n  71→### US-5: Stop Pipeline\n  72→作为授权用户，我可以使用 `/stop [target]` 停止运行中的管道。\n  73→\n  74→**Example**:\n  75→- `/stop` — 停止当前管道\n  76→- `/stop session-123` — 停止指定管道\n  77→\n  78→**Acceptance**:\n  79→- 确认停止操作\n  80→- 返回停止结果\n  81→\n  82→---\n  83→\n  84→### US-6: Error Guidance\n  85→作为用户，当我输入错误参数时，系统返回明确的修正建议。\n  86→\n  87→**Example**:\n  88→- `/pipeline xyz` → \"未知子命令 'xyz'。可用: run, status, logs, stop\"\n  89→\n  90→**Acceptance**:\n  91→- 参数错误有明确提示\n  92→- 提供正确的命令示例\n  93→\n  94→---\n  95→\n  96→### US-7: Authorization Guard\n  97→作为未授权用户，我无法调用管道命令，且收到统一拒绝提示。\n  98→\n  99→**Acceptance**:\n 100→- 所有管道命令需授权检查\n 101→- 统一拒绝消息（不暴露敏感信息）\n 102→\n 103→---\n 104→\n 105→## Non-Functional Requirements\n 106→\n 107→### NFR-1: Extensibility\n 108→- 命令路由层支持注册新命令\n 109→- 参数解析器可扩展\n 110→\n 111→### NFR-2: Testability\n 112→- Handler 接口可 mock\n 113→- 权限检查可 mock\n 114→\n 115→### NFR-3: Performance\n 116→- 命令解析 < 50ms\n 117→- 不阻塞 Telegram webhook\n 118→\n 119→---\n 120→\n 121→## Scope Boundaries\n 122→\n 123→### In Scope\n 124→- 命令解析与路由\n 125→- 参数规范化\n 126→- 权限检查\n 127→- 帮助文本生成\n 128→- 错误提示\n 129→\n 130→### Out of Scope\n 131→- 长任务执行（由 pipeline-control-service 处理）\n 132→- Pipeline 内部逻辑\n 133→- 持久化存储\n 134→- Web UI\n 135→\n 136→---\n 137→\n 138→## Command Reference\n 139→\n 140→| Command | Subcommands | Params | Handler |\n 141→|---------|-------------|--------|---------|\n 142→| `/pipeline` | run, status, logs, stop | `[target]`, `[--type=]` | pipelineHandler |\n 143→| `/bugfix` | — | `<target>` | bugfixHandler |\n 144→| `/planner` | run, status, logs | `[target]` | plannerHandler |\n 145→| `/status` | — | — | statusHandler |\n 146→| `/logs` | — | `[target]` | logsHandler |\n 147→| `/stop` | — | `[target]` | stopHandler |\n 148→\n 149→---\n 150→\n 151→## Alias Mapping\n 152→\n 153→| Alias | Maps To |\n 154→|-------|---------|\n 155→| `/p` | `/pipeline` |\n 156→| `/b` | `/bugfix` |\n 157→| `/s` | `/status` |\n 158→| `/l` | `/logs` |\n 159→\n 160→---\n 161→\n 162→## Decisions\n 163→\n 164→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 165→|----|------|----------|\n 166→| D1 | 2026-03-12 | `/planner` 为独立管道类型，行为同 `/pipeline`，默认 `type=planner` |\n 167→| D2 | 2026-03-12 | 复用现有 `isAllowedUser()` 进行授权检查，分级权限留作后续扩展 |\n 168→| D3 | 2026-03-12 | 日志 < 4000 字符分块发送，>= 4000 字符发送为文件 |\n 169→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde33ed3f9bdc09c71e868513fe14","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:41:30.185Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"36561b5f-3c80-4f9a-95d9-7b0cb49011dd","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_c325ccedf71d4af2aa80b7bd","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→import { Telegraf } from 'telegraf';\n   2→import { createReadStream } from 'node:fs';\n   3→import { access, stat } from 'node:fs/promises';\n   4→import os from 'node:os';\n   5→import path from 'node:path';\n   6→import { config } from '../config.js';\n   7→import { logger } from '../utils/logger.js';\n   8→import { isAllowedUser } from '../security/guard.js';\n   9→import { chatWithSession, resetSession } from '../services/chat-service.js';\n  10→import { captureScreenshot } from '../services/screenshot-service.js';\n  11→import { executeSystemCommand } from '../services/system-exec-service.js';\n  12→\n  13→const TELEGRAM_MSG_CHUNK_SIZE = 3800;\n  14→const STREAM_MIN_CHARS = 220;\n  15→const STREAM_FLUSH_INTERVAL_MS = 1200;\n  16→const TYPING_INTERVAL_MS = 3500;\n  17→const PHOTO_EXTENSIONS = new Set(['.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg', '.webp']);\n  18→const DOCUMENT_EXTENSIONS = new Set(['.pdf', '.txt', '.json', '.md', '.csv', '.log']);\n  19→const ALLOWED_FILE_EXTENSIONS = new Set([...PHOTO_EXTENSIONS, ...DOCUMENT_EXTENSIONS]);\n  20→const TELEGRAM_MAX_PHOTO_BYTES = 10 * 1024 * 1024;\n  21→const TELEGRAM_MAX_DOCUMENT_BYTES = 45 * 1024 * 1024;\n  22→const TELEGRAM_HANDLER_TIMEOUT_MS = 10 * 60 * 1000;\n  23→const TMP_DIR = path.resolve(os.tmpdir());\n  24→const HOME_DIR = path.resolve(os.homedir());\n  25→const DESKTOP_DIR = path.join(HOME_DIR, 'Desktop');\n  26→const DOWNLOADS_DIR = path.join(HOME_DIR, 'Downloads');\n  27→const DEFAULT_ALLOWED_FILE_ROOTS = [path.resolve(process.cwd()), DESKTOP_DIR, DOWNLOADS_DIR, TMP_DIR];\n  28→const DEFAULT_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS = [path.resolve(process.cwd()), DESKTOP_DIR, DOWNLOADS_DIR, TMP_DIR];\n  29→\n  30→function resolveConfiguredDirs(configuredDirs = [], fallbackDirs = []) {\n  31→  const normalized = configuredDirs\n  32→    .map((dir) => String(dir ?? '').trim())\n  33→    .filter(Boolean)\n  34→    .map((dir) => path.resolve(dir));\n  35→\n  36→  if (normalized.length > 0) {\n  37→    return [...new Set(normalized)];\n  38→  }\n  39→\n  40→  return [...new Set(fallbackDirs.map((dir) => path.resolve(String(dir))))];\n  41→}\n  42→\n  43→const ALLOWED_FILE_ROOTS = resolveConfiguredDirs(config.telegramFileAllowedRoots, DEFAULT_ALLOWED_FILE_ROOTS);\n  44→const FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS = resolveConfiguredDirs(config.telegramFileCandidateDirs, DEFAULT_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS);\n  45→\n  46→function splitMessage(text, chunkSize = TELEGRAM_MSG_CHUNK_SIZE) {\n  47→  const chunks = [];\n  48→  for (let i = 0; i < text.length; i += chunkSize) {\n  49→    chunks.push(text.slice(i, i + chunkSize));\n  50→  }\n  51→  return chunks;\n  52→}\n  53→\n  54→function sanitizeMarkerPath(raw) {\n  55→  return String(raw ?? '')\n  56→    .trim()\n  57→    .replace(/^['\"`]+/, '')\n  58→    .replace(/['\"`]+$/, '');\n  59→}\n  60→\n  61→function extractFileMarkers(text = '') {\n  62→  const fileRefs = [];\n  63→\n  64→  const withSendFileRemoved = text.replace(\n  65→    /(?:^|\\n)\\s*(?:[-*]\\s*)?`?SEND_FILE:([^\\n`]+)`?\\s*(?=\\n|$)/g,\n  66→    (_full, rawRef) => {\n  67→      const ref = sanitizeMarkerPath(rawRef);\n  68→      if (ref) {\n  69→        fileRefs.push(ref);\n  70→      }\n  71→      return '\\n';\n  72→    }\n  73→  );\n  74→\n  75→  const withImageRemoved = withSendFileRemoved.replace(/@image:([^\\s`]+)/g, (_full, rawRef) => {\n  76→    const ref = sanitizeMarkerPath(rawRef);\n  77→    if (ref) {\n  78→      fileRefs.push(ref);\n  79→    }\n  80→    return '';\n  81→  });\n  82→\n  83→  const withBacktickPathRemoved = withImageRemoved.replace(\n  84→    /`((?:\\/[^`\\n\\r]+)+\\.(?:png|jpg|jpeg|webp|pdf|txt|json|md|csv|log))`/gi,\n  85→    (_full, rawRef) => {\n  86→      const ref = sanitizeMarkerPath(rawRef);\n  87→      if (ref) {\n  88→        fileRefs.push(ref);\n  89→      }\n  90→      return '';\n  91→    }\n  92→  );\n  93→\n  94→  const withLabeledPathRemoved = withBacktickPathRemoved.replace(\n  95→    /(?:文件路径|path)\\s*[:：]\\s*((?:\\/[^\\n`\\r]+)+\\.(?:png|jpg|jpeg|webp|pdf|txt|json|md|csv|log))/gi,\n  96→    (_full, rawRef) => {\n  97→      const ref = sanitizeMarkerPath(rawRef);\n  98→      if (ref) {\n  99→        fileRefs.push(ref);\n 100→      }\n 101→      return '';\n 102→    }\n 103→  );\n 104→\n 105→  const withAbsolutePathLineRemoved = withLabeledPathRemoved.replace(\n 106→    /(?:^|\\n)\\s*(?:[-*]\\s*)?((?:\\/[^\\n`\\r]+)+\\.(?:png|jpg|jpeg|webp|pdf|txt|json|md|csv|log))\\s*(?=\\n|$)/gi,\n 107→    (_full, rawRef) => {\n 108→      const ref = sanitizeMarkerPath(rawRef);\n 109→      if (ref) {\n 110→        fileRefs.push(ref);\n 111→      }\n 112→      return '\\n';\n 113→    }\n 114→  );\n 115→\n 116→  return {\n 117→    fileRefs: [...new Set(fileRefs)],\n 118→    cleanedText: withAbsolutePathLineRemoved.replace(/\\n{3,}/g, '\\n\\n').trim()\n 119→  };\n 120→}\n 121→\n 122→function isPathWithinRoot(targetPath, rootPath) {\n 123→  const relative = path.relative(rootPath, targetPath);\n 124→  return relative === '' || (!relative.startsWith('..') && !path.isAbsolute(relative));\n 125→}\n 126→\n 127→function isAllowedFilePath(filePath) {\n 128→  const resolved = path.resolve(filePath);\n 129→  return ALLOWED_FILE_ROOTS.some((root) => isPathWithinRoot(resolved, root));\n 130→}\n 131→\n 132→function buildFileCandidates(normalizedPath) {\n 133→  if (path.isAbsolute(normalizedPath)) {\n 134→    return [normalizedPath];\n 135→  }\n 136→\n 137→  const baseName = path.basename(normalizedPath);\n 138→  const candidates = [\n 139→    path.resolve(process.cwd(), normalizedPath),\n 140→    ...FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS.map((dir) => path.resolve(dir, baseName))\n 141→  ];\n 142→\n 143→  return [...new Set(candidates)];\n 144→}\n 145→\n 146→async function resolveLocalFilePath(fileRef) {\n 147→  const normalized = sanitizeMarkerPath(fileRef);\n 148→  if (!normalized) {\n 149→    return { filePath: null, triedPaths: [], rejectReason: 'empty_path' };\n 150→  }\n 151→\n 152→  if (!path.isAbsolute(normalized)) {\n 153→    return { filePath: null, triedPaths: [], rejectReason: 'relative_path_not_allowed' };\n 154→  }\n 155→\n 156→  const candidates = buildFileCandidates(normalized);\n 157→\n 158→  for (const candidate of candidates) {\n 159→    try {\n 160→      await access(candidate);\n 161→      return { filePath: candidate, triedPaths: candidates };\n 162→    } catch {\n 163→      // ignore\n 164→    }\n 165→  }\n 166→\n 167→  return { filePath: null, triedPaths: candidates, rejectReason: 'not_found' };\n 168→}\n 169→\n 170→async function validateFileForTelegram(filePath) {\n 171→  const resolvedPath = path.resolve(filePath);\n 172→  if (!isAllowedFilePath(resolvedPath)) {\n 173→    return { ok: false, reason: `路径不在允许范围：${resolvedPath}` };\n 174→  }\n 175→\n 176→  const ext = path.extname(resolvedPath).toLowerCase();\n 177→  if (!ALLOWED_FILE_EXTENSIONS.has(ext)) {\n 178→    return { ok: false, reason: `不支持的文件类型：${ext || '(unknown)'}` };\n 179→  }\n 180→\n 181→  const fileStat = await stat(resolvedPath);\n 182→  const isPhoto = PHOTO_EXTENSIONS.has(ext);\n 183→  const maxSize = isPhoto ? TELEGRAM_MAX_PHOTO_BYTES : TELEGRAM_MAX_DOCUMENT_BYTES;\n 184→\n 185→  if (fileStat.size > maxSize) {\n 186→    return {\n 187→      ok: false,\n 188→      reason: `文件过大：${Math.ceil(fileStat.size / 1024 / 1024)}MB，限制 ${Math.floor(maxSize / 1024 / 1024)}MB`\n 189→    };\n 190→  }\n 191→\n 192→  return { ok: true, isPhoto, resolvedPath };\n 193→}\n 194→\n 195→function isTimeoutLikeError(message = '') {\n 196→  const normalized = String(message).toLowerCase();\n 197→  return normalized.includes('timed out') || normalized.includes('etimedout') || normalized.includes('timeout');\n 198→}\n 199→\n 200→function sleep(ms) {\n 201→  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms));\n 202→}\n 203→\n 204→async function sendTelegramFileByType(ctx, filePath, isPhoto) {\n 205→  if (isPhoto) {\n 206→    await ctx.replyWithPhoto({ source: createReadStream(filePath) }, { caption: path.basename(filePath) });\n 207→    return;\n 208→  }\n 209→\n 210→  await ctx.replyWithDocument({ source: createReadStream(filePath), filename: path.basename(filePath) });\n 211→}\n 212→\n 213→async function replyFiles(ctx, fileRefs = []) {\n 214→  const results = [];\n 215→\n 216→  for (const fileRef of fileRefs) {\n 217→    const { filePath, triedPaths, rejectReason } = await resolveLocalFilePath(fileRef);\n 218→    if (!filePath) {\n 219→      const reason = rejectReason || 'not_found';\n 220→      results.push({ fileRef, sent: false, reason, triedPaths });\n 221→      logger.warn({ fileRef, reason, triedPaths }, 'File unavailable for telegram upload');\n 222→      continue;\n 223→    }\n 224→\n 225→    try {\n 226→      const validation = await validateFileForTelegram(filePath);\n 227→      if (!validation.ok) {\n 228→        results.push({ fileRef, sent: false, reason: validation.reason, filePath, triedPaths });\n 229→        logger.warn({ fileRef, filePath, reason: validation.reason }, 'File validation failed for telegram upload');\n 230→        continue;\n 231→      }\n 232→\n 233→      const actualPath = validation.resolvedPath;\n 234→      let sent = false;\n 235→      let lastReason = '';\n 236→\n 237→      for (let attempt = 1; attempt <= 2; attempt += 1) {\n 238→        try {\n 239→          await sendTelegramFileByType(ctx, actualPath, validation.isPhoto);\n 240→          sent = true;\n 241→          logger.info(\n 242→            { fileRef, filePath: actualPath, as: validation.isPhoto ? 'photo' : 'document', attempt },\n 243→            'Telegram file sent'\n 244→          );\n 245→          break;\n 246→        } catch (error) {\n 247→          lastReason = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 248→          logger.warn(\n 249→            { fileRef, filePath: actualPath, err: lastReason, attempt },\n 250→            'Telegram file send attempt failed'\n 251→          );\n 252→\n 253→          if (attempt < 2 && isTimeoutLikeError(lastReason)) {\n 254→            await sleep(600);\n 255→            continue;\n 256→          }\n 257→\n 258→          break;\n 259→        }\n 260→      }\n 261→\n 262→      if (!sent) {\n 263→        results.push({ fileRef, sent: false, reason: lastReason || 'unknown_error', filePath: actualPath, triedPaths });\n 264→        logger.error({ fileRef, filePath: actualPath, err: lastReason }, 'Failed to send file to telegram');\n 265→        continue;\n 266→      }\n 267→\n 268→      results.push({ fileRef, sent: true, filePath: actualPath, triedPaths });\n 269→    } catch (error) {\n 270→      const reason = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 271→      results.push({ fileRef, sent: false, reason, filePath, triedPaths });\n 272→      logger.error({ fileRef, filePath, err: reason }, 'Failed to send file to telegram');\n 273→    }\n 274→  }\n 275→\n 276→  return results;\n 277→}\n 278→\n 279→async function safeReply(ctx, text) {\n 280→  try {\n 281→    await ctx.reply(text);\n 282→    return true;\n 283→  } catch (error) {\n 284→    const reason = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 285→    logger.error({ err: reason }, 'Failed to send telegram text reply');\n 286→    return false;\n 287→  }\n 288→}\n 289→\n 290→async function replyLargeText(ctx, text) {\n 291→  const chunks = splitMessage(text);\n 292→  for (const chunk of chunks) {\n 293→    const ok = await safeReply(ctx, chunk);\n 294→    if (!ok) {\n 295→      break;\n 296→    }\n 297→  }\n 298→}\n 299→\n 300→async function safeEditMessageText(ctx, messageId, text) {\n 301→  const nextText = text && text.trim() ? text : ' ';\n 302→\n 303→  try {\n 304→    await ctx.telegram.editMessageText(ctx.chat.id, messageId, undefined, nextText);\n 305→  } catch (error) {\n 306→    const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 307→    if (message.includes('message is not modified')) {\n 308→      return;\n 309→    }\n 310→    throw error;\n 311→  }\n 312→}\n 313→\n 314→function createEditableStreamPublisher(ctx) {\n 315→  let fullText = '';\n 316→  let renderedText = '';\n 317→  let pendingChars = 0;\n 318→  let lastFlushAt = 0;\n 319→  let flushChain = Promise.resolve();\n 320→  let activeMessage = null;\n 321→  let activeSegmentIndex = 0;\n 322→  let publishedMessageCount = 0;\n 323→\n 324→  async function ensureActiveMessage() {\n 325→    if (activeMessage) {\n 326→      return;\n 327→    }\n 328→    activeMessage = await ctx.reply('处理中...');\n 329→    activeSegmentIndex = 0;\n 330→    publishedMessageCount += 1;\n 331→  }\n 332→\n 333→  async function render(force = false) {\n 334→    const now = Date.now();\n 335→\n 336→    if (!force && pendingChars < STREAM_MIN_CHARS && now - lastFlushAt < STREAM_FLUSH_INTERVAL_MS) {\n 337→      return;\n 338→    }\n 339→\n 340→    if (fullText === renderedText) {\n 341→      pendingChars = 0;\n 342→      return;\n 343→    }\n 344→\n 345→    await ensureActiveMessage();\n 346→\n 347→    const segments = splitMessage(fullText);\n 348→    const targetLastIndex = Math.max(segments.length - 1, 0);\n 349→\n 350→    while (activeSegmentIndex < targetLastIndex) {\n 351→      const text = segments[activeSegmentIndex] ?? ' ';\n 352→      await safeEditMessageText(ctx, activeMessage.message_id, text);\n 353→\n 354→      activeMessage = await ctx.reply('继续输出中...');\n 355→      activeSegmentIndex += 1;\n 356→      publishedMessageCount += 1;\n 357→    }\n 358→\n 359→    const activeText = segments[targetLastIndex] ?? ' ';\n 360→    await safeEditMessageText(ctx, activeMessage.message_id, activeText);\n 361→\n 362→    renderedText = fullText;\n 363→    pendingChars = 0;\n 364→    lastFlushAt = now;\n 365→  }\n 366→\n 367→  function enqueueRender(force = false) {\n 368→    flushChain = flushChain.then(() => render(force));\n 369→  }\n 370→\n 371→  return {\n 372→    push(text) {\n 373→      const appendText = text ?? '';\n 374→      if (!appendText) {\n 375→        return;\n 376→      }\n 377→      fullText += appendText;\n 378→      pendingChars += appendText.length;\n 379→      enqueueRender(false);\n 380→    },\n 381→    setFinalText(text) {\n 382→      fullText = text ?? '';\n 383→      pendingChars = Math.max(pendingChars, STREAM_MIN_CHARS);\n 384→      enqueueRender(true);\n 385→    },\n 386→    async finish() {\n 387→      enqueueRender(true);\n 388→      await flushChain;\n 389→      return {\n 390→        outputLength: renderedText.length,\n 391→        messageCount: publishedMessageCount\n 392→      };\n 393→    }\n 394→  };\n 395→}\n 396→\n 397→function buildSessionId(ctx) {\n 398→  return String(ctx.chat.id);\n 399→}\n 400→\n 401→function ensureAllowed(ctx) {\n 402→  const userId = ctx.from?.id;\n 403→  if (!isAllowedUser(userId)) {\n 404→    throw new Error('当前账号未被授权使用该机器人。');\n 405→  }\n 406→}\n 407→\n 408→export function createTelegramBot() {\n 409→  const bot = new Telegraf(config.telegramBotToken, {\n 410→    handlerTimeout: TELEGRAM_HANDLER_TIMEOUT_MS\n 411→  });\n 412→\n 413→  bot.catch((error, ctx) => {\n 414→    const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 415→    logger.error({ err: message, chatId: ctx?.chat?.id, updateType: ctx?.updateType }, 'Unhandled error while processing telegram update');\n 416→  });\n 417→\n 418→  bot.start(async (ctx) => {\n 419→    await ctx.reply('PrizmClaw 已启动。可直接聊天，也可用 /screenshot 和 /exec。');\n 420→  });\n 421→\n 422→  bot.help(async (ctx) => {\n 423→    await ctx.reply('命令：\\n/reset - 清空会话\\n/screenshot - 获取本地截图\\n/exec <command> - 执行系统命令');\n 424→  });\n 425→\n 426→  bot.command('reset', async (ctx) => {\n 427→    try {\n 428→      ensureAllowed(ctx);\n 429→      resetSession({ channel: 'telegram', sessionId: buildSessionId(ctx) });\n 430→      await ctx.reply('已清空当前会话上下文。');\n 431→    } catch (error) {\n 432→      await ctx.reply(error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error));\n 433→    }\n 434→  });\n 435→\n 436→  bot.command('screenshot', async (ctx) => {\n 437→    try {\n 438→      ensureAllowed(ctx);\n 439→      await ctx.reply('正在获取截图。');\n 440→      const { buffer } = await captureScreenshot();\n 441→      await ctx.replyWithPhoto({ source: buffer }, { caption: '当前本地屏幕截图' });\n 442→    } catch (error) {\n 443→      const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 444→      logger.error({ err: message }, 'Failed to capture screenshot in telegram');\n 445→      await ctx.reply(`截图失败：${message}`);\n 446→    }\n 447→  });\n 448→\n 449→  bot.command('exec', async (ctx) => {\n 450→    try {\n 451→      ensureAllowed(ctx);\n 452→      const payload = ctx.message.text.replace('/exec', '').trim();\n 453→      if (!payload) {\n 454→        await ctx.reply('请提供命令，例如 /exec pwd');\n 455→        return;\n 456→      }\n 457→\n 458→      await ctx.reply('正在执行命令。');\n 459→      const result = await executeSystemCommand(payload);\n 460→      const output = [\n 461→        `exitCode: ${result.exitCode}`,\n 462→        result.stdout ? `stdout:\\n${result.stdout}` : 'stdout: (empty)',\n 463→        result.stderr ? `stderr:\\n${result.stderr}` : 'stderr: (empty)'\n 464→      ].join('\\n\\n');\n 465→\n 466→      await replyLargeText(ctx, output);\n 467→    } catch (error) {\n 468→      const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 469→      logger.error({ err: message }, 'Failed to exec command in telegram');\n 470→      await ctx.reply(`执行失败：${message}`);\n 471→    }\n 472→  });\n 473→\n 474→  bot.on('text', async (ctx) => {\n 475→    const sessionId = buildSessionId(ctx);\n 476→\n 477→    let typingTimer = null;\n 478→\n 479→    try {\n 480→      ensureAllowed(ctx);\n 481→      await ctx.sendChatAction('typing');\n 482→\n 483→      const streamPublisher = createEditableStreamPublisher(ctx);\n 484→      typingTimer = setInterval(() => {\n 485→        ctx.sendChatAction('typing').catch(() => undefined);\n 486→      }, TYPING_INTERVAL_MS);\n 487→\n 488→      const reply = await chatWithSession({\n 489→        channel: 'telegram',\n 490→        sessionId,\n 491→        message: ctx.message.text,\n 492→        realtimeHooks: {\n 493→          onStatus: ({ stage }) => {\n 494→            if (stage === 'running') {\n 495→              ctx.sendChatAction('typing').catch(() => undefined);\n 496→            }\n 497→          },\n 498→          onAssistantChunk: ({ text }) => {\n 499→            streamPublisher.push(text);\n 500→          }\n 501→        }\n 502→      });\n 503→\n 504→      const { fileRefs, cleanedText } = extractFileMarkers(reply);\n 505→      logger.info({ sessionId, fileRefsCount: fileRefs.length, fileRefs }, 'Parsed file markers from assistant reply');\n 506→      const finalText = cleanedText || (fileRefs.length > 0 ? '已执行，正在发送文件。' : '已执行。');\n 507→\n 508→      streamPublisher.setFinalText(finalText);\n 509→      const streamed = await streamPublisher.finish();\n 510→      if (streamed.outputLength === 0) {\n 511→        await replyLargeText(ctx, finalText);\n 512→      }\n 513→\n 514→      if (fileRefs.length > 0) {\n 515→        const fileSendResults = await replyFiles(ctx, fileRefs);\n 516→        const failed = fileSendResults.filter((item) => !item.sent);\n 517→\n 518→        if (failed.length === 0) {\n 519→          await safeReply(ctx, `已发送 ${fileSendResults.length} 个文件。`);\n 520→        } else {\n 521→          const failedList = failed\n 522→            .map((item) => {\n 523→              const reason =\n 524→                item.reason === 'relative_path_not_allowed'\n 525→                  ? '仅允许绝对路径，拒绝相对路径（请使用 SEND_FILE:/var/folders/.../xxx.png）'\n 526→                  : item.reason === 'not_found'\n 527→                    ? '文件不存在或不可访问（建议返回绝对路径，例如 SEND_FILE:/var/folders/.../xxx.png）'\n 528→                    : item.reason;\n 529→              const tried = Array.isArray(item.triedPaths) && item.triedPaths.length > 0 ? `；尝试路径：${item.triedPaths.join(' | ')}` : '';\n 530→              return `- SEND_FILE:${item.fileRef}${reason ? `（${reason}）` : ''}${tried}`;\n 531→            })\n 532→            .join('\\n');\n 533→          await safeReply(ctx, `以下文件发送失败，已附回原始引用：\\n${failedList}`);\n 534→          logger.warn({ sessionId, failed }, 'Some files failed to send to telegram');\n 535→        }\n 536→      }\n 537→    } catch (error) {\n 538→      const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 539→      logger.error({ err: message, sessionId }, 'Failed to process telegram message');\n 540→      await safeReply(ctx, `处理失败：${message}`);\n 541→    } finally {\n 542→      if (typingTimer) {\n 543→        clearInterval(typingTimer);\n 544→      }\n 545→    }\n 546→  });\n 547→\n 548→  return bot;\n 549→}\n 550→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde33ed3f9bdc09c71e868513fe14","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:41:30.189Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"9fc54022-adae-4270-942c-78fbe87505b8","session_id":"685aae5c-4106-4f0c-bd73-75d3c81ac2d9","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_ccf9bcfedcac4403a544d4da","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→import { executePipelineCommand } from '../pipeline-infra/script-runner.js';\n   2→\n   3→function buildRequest(params = {}, action) {\n   4→  return {\n   5→    pipelineType: params.pipelineType ?? 'feature',\n   6→    action,\n   7→    ...(params.targetId ? { targetId: params.targetId } : {}),\n   8→    ...(params.listPath ? { listPath: params.listPath } : {}),\n   9→    ...(params.envOverrides ? { envOverrides: params.envOverrides } : {}),\n  10→    ...(params.timeoutMs ? { timeoutMs: params.timeoutMs } : {})\n  11→  };\n  12→}\n  13→\n  14→export function createPipelineControlService({ runner = executePipelineCommand } = {}) {\n  15→  return {\n  16→    runner,\n  17→    async startPipeline(params) {\n  18→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'run'));\n  19→    },\n  20→    async getPipelineStatus(params) {\n  21→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'status'));\n  22→    },\n  23→    async stopPipeline(params) {\n  24→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'stop'));\n  25→    },\n  26→    async retryTarget(params) {\n  27→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'retry'));\n  28→    },\n  29→    async getPipelineLogs(params) {\n  30→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'logs'));\n  31→    },\n  32→    async resetTarget(params) {\n  33→      return runner(buildRequest(params, 'reset'));\n  34→    }\n  35→  };\n  36→}\n  37→\n  38→const defaultService = createPipelineControlService();\n  39→\n  40→export async function startPipeline(params) {\n  41→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  42→  return service.startPipeline(params);\n  43→}\n  44→\n  45→export async function getPipelineStatus(params) {\n  46→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  47→  return service.getPipelineStatus(params);\n  48→}\n  49→\n  50→export async function stopPipeline(params) {\n  51→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  52→  return service.stopPipeline(params);\n  53→}\n  54→\n  55→export async function retryTarget(params) {\n  56→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  57→  return service.retryTarget(params);\n  58→}\n  59→\n  60→export async function getPipelineLogs(params) {\n  61→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  62→  return service.getPipelineLogs(params);\n  63→}\n  64→\n  65→export async function resetTarget(params) {\n  66→  const service = createPipelineControlService({ runner: params?.runner ?? defaultService.runner });\n  67→  return service.resetTarget(params);\n  68→}\n  69→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde33ed3f9bdc09c71e868513fe14","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T18:41:30.196Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
