mation\n- US-6: Error guidance with clear suggestions\n- US-7: Authorization guard on all commands\n\n### Commands Implemented\n\n| Command | Aliases | Description |\n|---------|---------|-------------|\n| `/pipeline` | `/p` | Manage pipelines (run/status/logs/stop) |\n| `/bugfix` | `/b` | Start bugfix pipeline |\n| `/planner` | — | Manage planner pipelines |\n| `/status` | `/s` | Show running pipelines |\n| `/logs` | `/l` | View pipeline logs |\n| `/stop` | — | Stop running pipelines |\n\n### Verification\n\n- `npm test`: 105 tests pass (76 for F-002)\n- Code review: PASS\n- All 21 tasks completed"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":50274,"output_tokens":651,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:10:32.719Z","_requestId":"8512c899584843ddbcfa3594c4781204"}
